WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Hello this is Thomas with Automation Anonymous

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:05.000
So you want to learn how to automate the torture of those disgusting animals?

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Well here you go.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.000
First you need a subject.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:11.000
So get a hamster from something like a breeding pen or a plunger turret.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Hook that up to an industrial grinder.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.000
This industrial grinder turns your hamster into fresh meat.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
You can then cook that meat with a cooker.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.000
But be careful. If anything throws you an error its because that resource is not compatible with that machine.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:25.000
So just disconnect it and try a different resource.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.000
And you can combine resources in the combiner.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:33.000
For example combine the fur from the skinner as well as the cooked meat in the combiner and then you get burgers.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Throw those things on a shelf so you can sell them.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:37.000
You can also throw an auto interactor on it to automatically sell it.